Yamamoto K., Shimamura M., Degawa Y., & Yamada A.
Dual colonization of Mucoromycotina and Glomeromycotina fungi in the basal liverwort, Haplomitrium mnioides (Haplomitriopsida)

Yamamoto K., Shimamura M., Degawa Y., & Yamada A. 2019. Dual colonization of Mucoromycotina and Glomeromycotina fungi in the basal liverwort, Haplomitrium mnioides (Haplomitriopsida). Journal of Plant Research, .
A basal liverwort, Haplomitrium mnioides, shows morphologically distinguishable mycorrhiza-like structures with Endogonaceae, Densosporaceae (Endogonales, Mucoromycotina), and Glomeromycotina
